Name: LocalObjectReference_IdentifiableType
Description: A reference to the local object that is to be related to a depository object. If the relationship action is set to delete then no local object needs to be designated.

Name: LocalObjectReference_Versionable
Description: A reference to the local object that is to be related to a depository object. If the relationship action is set to delete then no local object needs to be designated.

Name: LocalObjectReference_Maintainable
Description: A reference to the local object that is to be related to a depository object. If the relationship action is set to delete then no local object needs to be designated.

Name: DepositoryObjectReference_IdentifiableType
Description: A reference to the deposited object.

Name: DepositoryObjectReference_Versionable
Description: A reference to the deposited object.

Name: DepositoryObjectReference_Maintainable
Description: A reference to the deposited object.

Name: RelationshipAction
Description: Provides a structured means of stating if the local object overrides (replaces) the depository object, adds information to the deposited object, deletes the content of the depository object without replacing it. or restricts access the deposited object by attaching an embargo or access restriction to it. Supports the use of a controlled vocabulary.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the link such as the reason for adding or changing local content. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.
